library(prophet)
library(tidyverse)

head_tail <- function(data, n = 5){
  stopifnot(is.data.frame(data))
  head(data, n = n) %>% print()
  cat(paste(rep("-", 100), collapse = ""), "\n")
  tail(data, n = n) %>% print()
}
